		<h2 class='diff-currentversion-title'>Revision as of 16:34, 3 September 2014</h2>
<div class="hatnote">This article is about the brand of electronic devices.  For its parent company, see <a href="/wiki/BlackBerry_Limited" title="BlackBerry Limited">BlackBerry Limited</a>.  For the fruit, see <a href="/wiki/Blackberry" title="Blackberry">Blackberry</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Blackberry_(disambiguation)" title="Blackberry (disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig">Blackberry (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
